<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَاحِد:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَن أَبِيه عَن أبي هُرَيْرَة:</span> صَلَاة فِي مَسْجِدي.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٥٧ - عبيد الله بن عبد الرَّحْمَن<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَاحِد:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">عَن عبيد بن حنين عَن أبي هُرَيْرَة:</span> <span class="c3">{قل هُوَ الله أحد}</span> وَجَبت.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>